2
00:00:14,805 --> 00:00:16,450
(M, South East Asia)

3
00:00:16,450 --> 00:00:17,970
Hello, sir.

4
00:00:20,900 --> 00:00:22,530
Don't you worry.

5
00:00:22,940 --> 00:00:25,450
Everyone is alright
with the goods for Guanhai.

6
00:00:29,100 --> 00:00:30,099
Got it.

7
00:00:30,100 --> 00:00:31,410
We're in this together, after all.

8
00:00:44,740 --> 00:00:46,130
Stand still.

9
00:00:46,460 --> 00:00:48,410
If you fall down again,

10
00:00:48,860 --> 00:00:50,570
I won't be able to fix you again.

11
00:00:52,740 --> 00:00:55,850
This is Mr. Wang's custom-made vase.

12
00:00:56,300 --> 00:00:58,290
And you broke it, Nong.

13
00:00:59,180 --> 00:01:02,850
Shouldn't you piece it back together?

14
00:01:17,740 --> 00:01:19,410
That's what we call art.

15
00:01:32,100 --> 00:01:34,170
It hurts so bad,

16
00:01:34,260 --> 00:01:35,410
Yi.

