158
00:08:06,780 --> 00:08:08,450
After all these years,

159
00:08:08,730 --> 00:08:10,840
I finally found the right painter
to do it.

160
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:14,250
I believe it'll be finished soon.

161
00:08:14,980 --> 00:08:16,130
Yun.

162
00:08:16,580 --> 00:08:18,050
I will

163
00:08:18,860 --> 00:08:20,170
